==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: living will
<hw>liv"ing will</hw>. <def>A document signed by an individual
expressing his/her desire that, in the event of an illness from which
there is no reasonable expectation of recovery, aggressive or
extraordinary measures to prolong life, such as resuscitation and
life-support equipment, should not be used.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Livistona</ent>⟦br⟧
